ime":"2020-05-29T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"每天與C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）、傑斯（Ryan Giggs）、史高斯（Paul Scholes）、雲佬（Ruud van Nistelrooy）和朗尼（Wayne Rooney）一起訓練，年輕球員一定受益匪淺。這是前曼聯球員大衛-鍾斯（David Jones）在18-21歲時獲得的特權。<br />\n<br />\n  大衛-鍾斯說：「這是我職業生涯開始的好地方，我對成為頂級球員有深刻的瞭解。當時，曼聯無疑是世界上最大的球會，每球員都想為他們和費格遜爵士效力。我當時19歲，在球會給我提供合約時，我已經訓練了大約6個月。」<br />\n<br />\n  「那時我還沒有經理人。堅尼（Roy Keane）和加利尼維利（Gary Neville）訓練後把我拉到一邊，並提出幫助我簽合約的事情。他們倆都很棒，我們在休息室裡，他們和我一起經歷了所有的事情，那是一次值得學習的經驗，」大衛-鍾斯說：「他們想我得到一份公平的合約，實際上是他倆代表我同經理談判了合約。」<br />\n<br />\n  鍾斯在幾天後簽字新合約。他最後說：「簽約後，我為他們買了兩瓶酒以表示感謝，這是我一生中所要付出的最便宜的佣金！」"},{"pid":"79359546df18264dc749f06562a846f3547cc6f4","tid":2042083,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"香港獨立都del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdaec12cef2d5c385121b09d4ba950e9f117c22","tid":2042083,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7873dfe0a3c25ef73f3855100ea1b8ed344b43f","tid":2042083,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79359546df18264dc749f06562a846f3547cc6f4","tid":2042083,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"香港獨立都del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a900bddbaf297aeb060aa31af11288ce8aa42951","tid":2042083,"uid":12591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79359546df18264dc749f06562a846f3547cc6f4","tid":2042083,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"香港獨立都del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite